Meet <b>Angelbaby</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Angelbaby lives at <a href='/home/?user=angelbaby271'>12569 Bridge Row</a> in one of Golden Valley's quaint old farmhouses.  She's been enjoying the laid-back rural lifestyle among her neighborhood's rolling green fields and wooded hills since she moved in on October 19, 2005.<br><br>Angelbaby is a born performer.  She's very outgoing and loves to sing.  One of her dreams is to perform her very own songs on her light blue, gold, and silver guitar in front of a huge crowd of screaming fans.  Angelbaby especially loves rock music and is very inspired by the songs in her vast collection of classic rock, modern rock, and soft rock CDs.  She hopes that someday her music will inspire other people, too!<br><br>Just because she enjoys hard rock doesn't mean that Angelbaby doesn't also have a caring side, though.  She often spends time volunteering at animal shelters and even drops by the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=9">Pet Palace</a> in <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/main_map.phtml?location=downtown">Downtown Millsberry</a> to clean the animals' cages, play with them, and take them for walks.  Angelbaby also has many pets of her own that she loves spending time with.  In addition to domesticated animals like dogs and cats, Angelbaby is very interested in more exotic animals, which is why she can often be found at the zoo, admiring beautiful creatures and learning about their lives in the wild.<br><br>In her spare time, Angelbaby likes to explore other interests, such as computers and movies.  She loves spending an afternoon learning new programming tricks or designing a website for a friend.  When Angelbaby wants to unwind after a particularly challenging session at her computer, she usually heads to the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/communitycenter/pool.phtml">pool</a> for a relaxing swim or the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/theater.phtml">theater</a> in the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/">Downtown Entertainment Complex</a> to catch the latest movie.<br><br>Thanks for being a good citizen, Angelbaby, and congratulations on being Millsberry's Citizen of the Week!</div>
